Hi everyone,
        The internship team is planning to have a fundae session regarding
internships tomorrow (20/04/16) at 6 pm in CRC 101.
This fundae session will cover both industrial internships and research
internships(6 pm to 7 pm for industrial internships and 7 pm to 8:30 for
research internships)
In industrial internships,resume making fundae session followed by the
basic timeline that will be followed the next year for internships will be
elaborated.

In the next part of the session,seniors who already got research intern
with scholarships through DAAD,Mitacs,S.N.Bose will explain about the
 procedure and the timeline they followed for their preparation.
This is a very  important session as it will give the fundamental idea
regarding the next year's internship season.
So all the second years,do attend the session!!

